77  public override FutureMove Think(Board board, CancellationToken ct)
78  {
79  // Bad move to return
80  FutureMove futureMove;
81 
82  // Determine which bad move to return
83  switch (badMove)
84  {
85  case BadMove.AboveColumn:
86  futureMove =
87  new FutureMove(board.cols, board.Turn.Shape());
88  break;
89  case BadMove.BelowColumn:
90  futureMove = new FutureMove(-1, board.Turn.Shape());
91  break;
92  case BadMove.Repeat:
93  futureMove = new FutureMove(0, board.Turn.Shape());
94  break;
95  case BadMove.NoMove:
96  futureMove = FutureMove.NoMove;
97  break;
98  case BadMove.Exception:
99  throw new Exception(String.Format(
100  "{0} throwing an exception for testing purposes.",
101  nameof(BadMoveAIThinker)));
102  default:
103  throw new InvalidOperationException(
104  $"Invalid use of {nameof(BadMoveAIThinker)}");
105  }
106 
107  // Return the bad move
108  return futureMove;
109  }
